<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203330>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus photos of new Docosia species. a, b, Docosia rameli sp. nov. (a = male, b = female); c, d, Docosia muranica sp. nov. (c = male, terminalia detached, d = female, terminalia detached); e, Docosia kerkini sp. nov. (male, terminalia detached). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203331>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Docosia muranica sp. nov., male terminalia. a, lateral view; b, posterior view; c, ventral view of gonostylus; d, dorsal view of tergite IX; e, dorsal view of cerci; f, ventral view of aedeagal complex. Scale bar = 0.1 mm. Abbreviations: aed = aedeagus; gc = gonocoxite; gc vam = ventroapical margin of gonocoxite; gst vl = ventral lobe of gonostylus; gst dl I = ventral part of dorsal lobe of gonostylus; gst dl II = dorsal part of dorsal lobe of gonostylus; par = paramere; ret = combs of retinacula." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

